videos.description: Playing without Russell Westbrook and Carmelo Anthony, Paul George can't do enough and the Thunder fall to the Lakers 106-81. Los Angeles improves to 12-4 since January 7.
videos.headline: Lakers take down shorthanded Thunder

videos.description: Lakers forward Julius Randle explains his thoughts on a busy trade deadline day for the team and what he expects going forward.
